      "text": "```text\nRequest (subject) ──→ Plan (subject) ──→ Review (subject)\n        │                    │                    │\n   set by user,         inherited from       inherited from\n   agent-generated,     parent request       parent plan\n   or fallback\n```text\n\n- The plan creation code (`RequestProcessor.createPlanFromResponse`) copies the request's `subject` into the plan's frontmatter.\n- The review creation code (`ReviewCommands`/review generator) copies the plan's `subject` into the review's frontmatter.\n- If a parent entity has no subject (backward compatibility), the child entity's subject remains `undefined`.\n\n---\n\n## Refactoring Plan\n\n### Step 1. Schema & Type Changes (The Foundation)\n\n**Objective**: Add `subject` to all entity type definitions.\n\n**Files to modify:**",
